":20170,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T03:39:06.000Z","msg":"喜聞樂見<br />\n同時其實同係成個生產鏈斷咗<br />\n呢壇嘢之後，相信全球產業都唔敢將生產環節擺晒落中國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T03:40:38.000Z","msg":"呢個一定<br />\n中國就算呢單嘢解決咗，個經濟都好難回復返去之前咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ea0b4c5072d98157981ddd324b284e991dd70c","tid":1888042,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T03:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e43a544fe36d22bbeb157e2.jpg/g3VOlZQ8eoG4azaxTZ2bCalehxDRWVRaXydXvF8nV7w?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e43a544fe36d22bbeb157e2.jpg%2Fg3VOlZQ8eoG4azaxTZ2bCalehxDRWVRaXydXvF8nV7w%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=dfd4c177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.tenor.com/images/e10c12f7c3e996c001949ab7ae551f47/tenor.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.tenor.com%2Fimages%2Fe10c12f7c3e996c001949ab7ae551f47%2Ftenor.gif&h=b24d49c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二氧化硫，（英語：sulphur dioxide , sulfur dioxide）化學式是SO2。是最常見的硫氧化物。無色氣體，有強烈刺激性氣味。大氣主要污染物之一。<br />\n由於煤和石油通常都含有硫化合物，因此燃燒時會生成二氧化硫。當二氧化硫溶於水中，會形成亞硫酸（酸雨的主要成分）。若把SO2進一步氧化，通常在催化劑如二氧化氮的存在下，便會生成硫酸。[1]這就是對使用這些燃料作為能源的環境效果的擔心的原因之一。"},{"pid":"baaa860c36cbe79ec1a627152ecbc2104aeff3ee","tid":1888042,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T03:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a055be0404792fc8c19800322ca5611d7b0a5b2","tid":1888042,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T03:42:38.000Z","msg":"中國又為人類和平作出偉大貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a54b260c563232db28a208ace59d4353605ef52","tid":1888042,"uid":26752